flowchart TB
  %% Salesforce CPQ Quote Process Template
  %% Customize for Salesforce CPQ or Steelbrick implementation

  Start((New Quote)) --> CreateQuote[Create Quote from Opportunity]

  CreateQuote --> AddProducts{Add Products?}

  AddProducts -->|Manual| ProductSelection[Manual Product Selection]
  AddProducts -->|Guided| GuidedSelling[Guided Selling Flow]

  ProductSelection --> ConfigureProducts[Configure Products]
  GuidedSelling --> ConfigureProducts

  ConfigureProducts --> AddOptions{Add Options/Bundles?}

  AddOptions -->|Yes| OptionSelection[Select Options & Bundles]
  AddOptions -->|No| ApplyDiscounts

  OptionSelection --> ApplyDiscounts[Apply Discounts & Promotions]

  ApplyDiscounts --> CalculatePrice[Calculate Pricing]

  CalculatePrice --> CheckApproval{Requires Approval?}

  CheckApproval -->|Yes| SubmitApproval[Submit for Approval]
  CheckApproval -->|No| GenerateDocument

  SubmitApproval --> ApprovalDecision{Approved?}

  ApprovalDecision -->|Approved| GenerateDocument[Generate Quote Document]
  ApprovalDecision -->|Rejected| RevisePricing[Revise Pricing]
  ApprovalDecision -->|Recalled| RevisePricing

  RevisePricing --> ApplyDiscounts

  GenerateDocument --> ReviewQuote[Review with Customer]

  ReviewQuote --> CustomerDecision{Customer Decision?}

  CustomerDecision -->|Accepted| CreateContract[Create Contract]
  CustomerDecision -->|Negotiate| RevisePricing
  CustomerDecision -->|Rejected| CloseQuote[Close Quote - Lost]

  CreateContract --> GenerateOrders[Generate Orders]

  GenerateOrders --> End((Quote Processed))
  CloseQuote --> End
